'''飓风丽丽'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Lili}}）是[[2002年大西洋飓风季|2002年大西洋飓风季]]造成人员丧生和财产损失均仅次于[[飓风伊西多尔|飓风伊西多尔]]的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，两场飓风间隔仅有一星期，影响的区域基本相同，并且是本季最强烈的两场风暴。丽丽源自9月21日大西洋开放海域上空的[[热带扰动|热带扰动]]，是本季第12场获得命名的风暴、第4场飓风和第2场大型飓风。系统向西移动，以热带风暴强度吹袭[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]，然后进入加勒比地区。受[[古巴|古巴]]南部的[[风切变|风切变]]影响，气旋在西进期间一度消散，之后又在垂直风切变减弱后再生。风暴转向西北，于10月1日达到[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的二级飓风标准，再于当天两次从古巴西部[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，然后进入[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]。10月2日，丽丽[[快速增强|急剧强化]]，于当天下午达到四级飓风强度。此后气旋迅速减弱，于10月3日以一级飓风强度吹袭[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]，在朝内陆行进期间逐渐减弱，最终于10月6日消散。<ref name="TCR">{{Cite report | author = Miles Lawrence | title = Tropical Cyclone Report: Hurricane Lili | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | work = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | deadurl = no | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304043136/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL132002_Lili.pdf | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|Florida]] | year = 2002 | accessdate = 2016-04-05 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL132002_Lili.pdf | date =  }}</ref>

飓风在途经加勒比地区期间引发大范围破坏，其中农作物和建筑质量欠佳的民宅灾情最重<ref name="caribmud">{{Cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | title = Lili leaves trail of destruction in Eastern Caribbean | newspaper = Jamaica Observer | url = http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/32586_Lili-leaves-trail-of-destruction-in-Eastern-Caribbean | year = 2002 | accessdate = 2016-04-05 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304042835/http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/32586_Lili-leaves-trail-of-destruction-in-Eastern-Caribbean }}</ref>。[[泥石流|泥石流]]在多山岛屿相当常见，并以[[海地|海地]]和[[牙买加|牙买加]]最为典型<ref name="USAtoday1">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | title = Lili killed 4 in Haiti;deaths unreported for a week | work = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | accessdate = 2016-04-05 | publisher = Gannett Co. Inc. | archivedate = 2015-08-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150820063623/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/news/2002/2002-10-05-lili-haiti.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/news/2002/2002-10-05-lili-haiti.htm | date = 2002-10-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。丽丽导致美国在墨西哥湾的石油开采中断，路易斯安那州部分地区受到严重破坏，该州南部近海的多个屏障岛或湿地也受到重创。气旋自始至终一共夺走15条人命，损失总额高达9.25亿美元（2002年美元）。<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="costliest">{{cite report | work = National Hurricane Center/National Climatic Data Center | last1 = Blake | first1 = Eric S | last2 = Landsea | first2 = Christopher W | last3 = Gibney | first3 = Ethan J | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | deadurl = no | date = 2011-08 | title = Costliest U.S. Hurricanes 1900 - 2010 (unadjusted): Table 3a: The 30 costliest mainland United States tropical cyclones, 1900-2010, (not adjusted for inflation) | type = NOAA Technical Memorandum NWS NHC-6 | accessdate = 2016-04-05 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/nws-nhc-6.pdf | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service | page = 11 | format = PDF | location = Miami, Florida | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306133015/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/nws-nhc-6.pdf }}</ref>

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Lili 2002 track.png}}
9月16日，一股[[东风波|东风波]]离开非洲西海岸进入[[大西洋|大西洋]]。东风波催生出[[热带扰动|热带扰动]]，扰动天气在9月20日行进至非洲和加勒比地区中途海域时发展出下层环流中心。次日，系统的组织结构已有显著改善，成为[[2002年大西洋飓风季|本季]]第十三号热带低气压。<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="nhcadv#1">{{Cite report | author1 = Lixion Avila | author2 = Eric Blake | title = Tropical Depression Thirteen Advisory Number 1 | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | year = 2002 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002082738/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public.001.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2008-03-22 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public.001.html | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | date =  }}</ref>气旋以每小时超过32公里的速度西进，在途经[[向风群岛|向风群岛]]期间升级成[[热带气旋|热带风暴]]并获名“丽丽”（{{lang|en|Lili}}）<ref name="nhcadv#2">{{Cite report | author = Stacey Stewart | title = Tropical Storm Lili Intermediate Advisory Number 9A | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | date = 2002-09-23 | accessdate = 2016-04-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306140952/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public_a.009.html | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public_a.009.html | archivedate = 2016-03-06 }}</ref>。风暴向西进入[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]，在此期间继续增强，于9月24日早上达到风速每小时110公里的第一波强度高峰<ref name="nhcadv#13">{{Cite report | author = Stacey Stewart | accessdate = 2016-04-05 | date = 2002-09-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306134913/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public.013.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public.013.html | title = Tropical Storm Lili Advisory Number 13 | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2016-03-06 }}</ref>。但在强烈南向[[风切变|垂直风切变]]的影响下<ref name="nhcdis#15">{{Cite report | author1 = Brian Jarvinen | author2 = Robert Molleda | title = Tropical Storm Lili Discussion Number 15 | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | year = 2002 | accessdate = 2016-04-05 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303223325/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al132002.discus.015.html | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al132002.discus.015.html | date =  }}</ref>，丽丽接下来突然开始减弱，持续风速当天就大幅下跌至每小时64公里<ref name="nhcadv#15">{{Cite report | author1 = Brian Jarvinen | author2 = Robert Molleda | title = Tropical Storm Lili Advisory Number 15 | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | date = 2002-09-24 | accessdate = 2016-04-05 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public.015.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306121555/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public.015.html | archivedate = 2016-03-06 }}</ref>。次日清晨，气旋退化成开放式东风波，并在此状态下保持了近两天时间<ref name="TCR" />。

9月26日晚，丽丽在[[牙买加|牙买加]]附近再生，并在朝[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向小幅转向的同时逐渐强化<ref name="TCR" />。9月30日，系统在经过[[开曼群岛|开曼群岛]]后不久升级成飓风<ref name="nhcadv#36">{{Cite report | author = James Franklin | title = Hurricane Lili Advisory Number #36 | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | date = 2002-09-30 | accessdate = 2016-04-05 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public.036.html | archivedate = 2015-12-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151217185143/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public.036.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>。风暴继续向西北偏西前进并增强，并于次日以二级飓风强度先后从[[青年岛|青年岛]]和[[比那尔德里奥|比那尔德里奥]]附近[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]<ref name="nhcadv#40A">{{Cite report | author = Jack Beven | title = Hurricane Lili Intermediate Advisory Number 40A | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | year = 2002-10-01 | accessdate = 2016-04-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303211109/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public_a.040.html | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public_a.040.html | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | date =  }}</ref>。当晚，气旋强度在登陆后基本得以保持，然后进入[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]上空<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="nhcadv#41">{{Cite report | author = Jack Beven | title = Hurricane Lili Advisory Number 41 | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | year = 2002 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303204610/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public.041.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-04-05 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public.041.html | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | date =  }}</ref>。

飓风转向西北并加快移动速度，于10月2日在[[新奥尔良|新奥尔良]]东南偏南方向约587公里洋面成为[[热带气旋风级|大型飓风]]<ref name="nhcadv#44">{{Cite report | author = Jack Beven | title = Hurricane Lili Advisory Number 44 | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | date = 2002-10-02 | accessdate = 2016-04-05 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303212324/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public.044.html | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public.044.html }}</ref>。由于外流良好，墨西哥湾内[[海面温度|海面温度]]也比较高，风暴继续增强<ref name="nhcdisc#44">{{Cite report | author = Jack Beven | title = Hurricane Lili Discussion Number 44 | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | date = 2002-10-02 | accessdate = 2016-04-05 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303171549/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al132002.discus.044.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al132002.discus.044.html }}</ref>。当天下午，丽丽达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]每小时233公里的最高强度，已满足[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]的四级飓风标准<ref name="nhcadv#45">{{Cite report | author = Jack Beven | title = Hurricane Lili Special Advisory Number 45 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303170251/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public.045.html | deadurl = no | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | date = 2002-10-02 | accessdate = 2016-04-05 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public.045.html }}</ref>。

风暴在最高强度下保持的时间很短，10月3日清晨行进至路易斯安那州[[弗米利恩堂区_(路易斯安那州)|弗米利恩堂区]]的[[因特拉科斯特尔城_(路易斯安那州)|因特拉科斯特尔城]]（{{lang|en|Intracoastal City}}）附近海域时，丽丽开始因水温降低、垂直风切变增多<ref>{{cite news | author = Chris Cappella | publisher = Gannett Co. Inc. | work = USA Today | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/news/2002/2002-10-04-lili-weakened.htm | archivedate = 2016-01-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160128034136/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/news/2002/2002-10-04-lili-weakened.htm | title = Scientists don't yet know why Lili suddenly collapsed | accessdate = 2016-04-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，并且西南象限还受到干燥空气的缓慢侵蚀而快速弱化<ref>{{cite report | author = Adele Marie Babin | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303205249/http://etd.lsu.edu/docs/available/etd-11082004-100236/unrestricted/Babin_thesis.pdf | url = http://etd.lsu.edu/docs/available/etd-11082004-100236/unrestricted/Babin_thesis.pdf | title = Characteristics of Hurricane Lili’S Intensity Changes | accessdate = 2016-04-05 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = PDF | date = 2004-12 | publisher = [[路易斯安那州立大学|Louisiana State University]] }}</ref><ref name="nhcadv#48">{{Cite report | author = Richard Pasch | title = Hurricane Lili Advisory Number 48 | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | date = 2002-10-03 | accessdate = 2016-04-05 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public.048.html | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303214152/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public.048.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>。到登陆时，飓风的最大持续风速已大幅回落至每小时145公里<ref name="nhcadv#49">{{Cite report | author = Lixion Avila | title = Hurricane Lili Advisory Number 49 | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | year = 2002 | accessdate = 2016-04-05 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public.049.html | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303184148/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public.049.html | date =  }}</ref>。减弱期间，丽丽的内层[[风眼|风眼]]也在登陆前坍塌<ref name="TCR" />。风暴继续向东北偏北方向深入内陆，最终于10月6日在[[阿肯色州|阿肯色州]]和[[田纳西州|田纳西州]]边界附近被[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]吸收而消散<ref name="TCR" />。

== 防灾措施 ==
[[File:Lili2002sep30NHCforecast.GIF|thumb]]对飓风丽丽的移动路线预测，其中红色部分代表[[热带气旋警告|飓风警告]]区域，蓝色代表热带风暴警告区域，白色部分表示气旋可能经过的地区，其中的黑色直线和圆点表示飓风中心最可能经过的路径。]]

9月22日，[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]部分地区接获[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴观察预警]]，并于次日下午升级成热带风暴警告。9月23日晚气旋过境后，上述警告均予中止。<ref name="TCR" />接下来的一星期里，[[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]、牙买加、古巴、开曼群岛和[[尤卡坦半岛|尤卡坦半岛]]都曾在部分时段收到风暴公告<ref name="TCR" />。10月1日，[[美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区|美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区]]收到飓风观察预警或热带风暴观察预警，再于次日早上升级成飓风警告或热带风暴警告<ref name="TCR" />。10月3日丽丽经过后，所有警告全部取消<ref name="nhcadv#49B">{{Cite report | author = Lixion Avila | title = Tropical Storm Lili Intermediate Advisory Number 49B | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | date = 2002-10-03 | accessdate = 2016-04-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303184421/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public_b.049.html | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al132002.public_b.049.html | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>。

气旋袭击各个岛屿时尚处弱热带风暴强度，因此当地采取的防灾措施力度很小。[[圣文森特岛|圣文森特岛]]和[[格林纳丁斯岛|格林纳丁斯岛]]有约200人在丽丽来袭前离开家园<ref name="caribmud" />。牙买加所有的学校都在风暴来临前关闭，岛上还开设有17个公共避难所<ref name="jamaicamon">{{Cite news | author = Horace Helps | title = News: Caribbean: Tropical Storm Lili — September 2002, Hurricane Lili belts Caymans, 4 dead in Jamaica | publisher = Relief Web | year = 2002 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130603100407/http://reliefweb.int/report/cayman-islands/hurricane-lili-belts-caymans-4-dead-jamaica | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/cayman-islands/hurricane-lili-belts-caymans-4-dead-jamaica | accessdate = 2008-04-06 | archivedate = 2013-06-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

面对来袭的气旋，古巴采取大量措施防灾减灾。[[关塔那摩湾|关塔那摩湾]]的军方人员准备将关押的[[基地组织|基地组织]]及[[塔利班|塔利班]]囚犯转移<ref name="guantanamo">{{cite news | agency = [[路透社|Reuters]] | title = United States to move Cuba base detainees if storm nears | publisher = [[卫报|The Guardian]] | accessdate = 2016-04-06 | url = http://www.theguardian.com/world/2002/sep/25/1 | location = [[伦敦|London]] | date = 2002-09-25 | archivedate = 2016-03-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307163352/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2002/sep/25/1 }}</ref>。共有13万古巴公民在风暴来袭前撤离家园，其中大部分来自该国西部<ref name="cubaevac">{{Cite news | agency = Associated Press | title = Gulf Coast under Lili watch | newspaper = The St. Petersburg Times | date = 2002-10-02 | accessdate = 2016-04-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303170738/http://www.sptimes.com/2002/10/02/Weather/Gulf_Coast_under_Lili.shtml | url = http://www.sptimes.com/2002/10/02/Weather/Gulf_Coast_under_Lili.shtml | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | location = St. Petersburg, FL }}</ref>。

