飓风来袭前，美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区采取强力防灾措施，气象机构一度预计丽丽会以四级飓风登陆，所以防灾工作变得更加紧迫。[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]和路易斯安那州有超过50万人离开家园，路易斯安那州[[伊比利亚堂区_(路易斯安那州)|伊比利亚堂区]]所有居民全部撤离<ref name="latxevac">{{cite news | author = Jeffrey Gettleman | title = Thousands Seek Safety as Hurricane Nears Gulf Coast | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | accessdate = 2016-04-06 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2002/10/03/us/thousands-seek-safety-as-hurricane-nears-gulf-coast.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160309211637/http://www.nytimes.com/2002/10/03/us/thousands-seek-safety-as-hurricane-nears-gulf-coast.html | date = 2002-10-03 | archivedate = 2016-03-09 }}</ref>。路易斯安那州共有20万人疏散<ref name="latxevac" /><ref name="cnn">{{cite news | author = Cable News Network | title = Red Cross shelters thousands from the storm | publisher = Cable News Network | accessdate = 2016-04-06 | archivedate = 2008-04-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080405105201/http://archives.cnn.com/2002/WEATHER/10/03/lili.states/index.html | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2002/WEATHER/10/03/lili.states/ | date = 2002-10-03 }}</ref>。德克萨斯州、路易斯安那州、[[密西西比州|密西西比州]]和[[阿拉巴马州|阿拉巴马州]]开设的115个红十字会避难所中至少配备有2000名工作人员<ref name="redcross2000">{{Cite news | author = Bonnie Gillespie | title = Team Louisiana Weathers Hurricane Lili | year = 2002 | publisher = The Red Cross | accessdate = 2008-04-05 | url = http://www.redcross.org/news/ds/hurricanes/021008lili.html | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080405105201/http://archives.cnn.com/2002/WEATHER/10/03/lili.states/index.html | archivedate = 2008-04-05 }}</ref>，有超过2万人进入其中躲避<ref name="cnn" />。[[国际红十字与红新月运动|红十字会]]还向上述各州送去超过16万顿膳食<ref name="redcross2000" />。德克萨斯州共有3000名囚犯转移到更加安全的内陆地点<ref name="latxevac" />。由于[[肯尼迪航天中心|肯尼迪航天中心]]也受到气旋威胁，[[亚特兰提斯号航天飞机|亚特兰提斯号航天飞机]]的发射被迫延迟5天之久，这也是历史上[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]进行的火箭发射首次因[[休斯敦|休斯敦]]的天气问题推迟<ref name="atlantis">{{Cite news | author = David Cohen | date = 2002-10-02 | title = Hurricane Lili closes shuttle Mission Control | publisher = NewScientist | accessdate = 2012-04-21 | archivedate = 2015-05-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150513054245/http://www.newscientist.com/article/dn2873-hurricane-lili-closes-shuttle-mission-control.html | url = https://www.newscientist.com/article/dn2873-hurricane-lili-closes-shuttle-mission-control/ | deadurl = no }}</ref>。预警区域各地的商店在飓风来袭前忙得不可开交，路易斯安那州[[新伊比利亚_(路易斯安那州)|新伊比利亚]]的多家五金店卖到断货<ref name="hardwareIb">{{Cite news | author = KXAS | title = Hurricane Lili Makes Landfall Into Louisiana Coast | publisher = National Broadcasting Company | date = 2002-10-03 | accessdate = 2008-03-28 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20021016113739/http://www.nbc5i.com/news/1698445/detail.html | archivedate = 2002-10-16 | url = http://www.nbc5i.com/news/1698445/detail.html }}</ref>，[[拉法叶_(路易斯安那州)|拉法叶]]的许多商店也有类似情况<ref name="lafprep">{{Cite news | author = Mike Brassfield | title = Hurricane Lili runs out of steam | newspaper = The St. Petersburg Times | date = 2002-10-04 | accessdate = 2016-04-06 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303171404/http://www.sptimes.com/2002/10/04/Worldandnation/Hurricane_Lili_runs_o.shtml | url = http://www.sptimes.com/2002/10/04/Worldandnation/Hurricane_Lili_runs_o.shtml }}</ref>。

大学活动也因丽丽受到影响，[[南方大学_(美国)|南方大学]]被迫停课4天<ref name="SU">{{Cite news | author = Gabrielle Maple | title = Back to Back | publisher = The Southern Digest | year = 2002 | accessdate = 2007-06-07 | url = http://media.www.southerndigest.com/media/storage/paper950/news/2002/10/08/News/Back-To.Back-2233030.shtml | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.li/20070607060016/http://media.www.southerndigest.com/media/storage/paper950/news/2002/10/08/News/Back-To.Back-2233030.shtml | archivedate = 2007-06-07 }}</ref>，身在德克萨斯州[[加尔维斯敦_(得克萨斯州)|加尔维斯敦]][[德克萨斯州农工大学|德克萨斯州农工大学]]的20名学生疏散到该校在[[大学城_(得克萨斯州)|大学城]]的校园<ref name="A@M">{{Cite web | author = Jeremy Osborne | title = Texas Task Force Sent to Galveston | publisher = The Batt | date = 2002-10-03 | accessdate = 2013-08-16 | archiveurl = https://archive.li/20130816082216/http://www.thebatt.com/2.8500/texas-task-force-sent-to-galveston-1.1212064%23.Ug3hCX3LfK4 | archivedate = 2013-08-16 | deadurl = yes | url = http://media.www.thebatt.com/media/storage/paper657/news/2002/10/03/FrontPage/Texas.Task.Force.Sent.To.Galveston-515455.shtml }}</ref>。[[南阿拉巴马大学|南阿拉巴马大学]]还有两场学术活动在气旋袭击前取消<ref name="USA">{{Cite web | author = Jeff Roper | title = Hurricane Lili cancels two games | publisher = The Vanguard | date = 2002-10-07 | accessdate = 2011-07-17 | archivedate = 2011-07-17 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.li/20110717180245/http://www.usavanguard.com/2.2307/hurricane-lili-cancels-two-games-1.186785 | url = http://media.www.usavanguard.com/media/storage/paper973/news/2002/10/07/Sports/Hurricane.Lili.Cancels.Two.Games-2618639.shtml }}</ref>。

