无论是致死人数还是损失数额，飓风丽丽在2002年大西洋飓风季中都排第2，仅次于夺走22条人命，经济损失高达13亿美元的[[飓风伊西多尔|飓风伊西多尔]]<ref name="nhcyearly">{{Cite report | author1 = Lixion Avila | author2 = Jack Beven | author3 = James Franklin | author4 = Miles Lawrence | author5 = Richard Pasch | author6 = Stacey Stewart | title = Summary of Tropical Cyclone Activity of 2002 | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303212019/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/tws/MIATWSAT_nov.html | deadurl = no | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | year = 2002 | accessdate = 2016-04-06 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/tws/MIATWSAT_nov.html | date =  }}</ref>。丽丽在加勒比地区各个岛屿共计夺走13条人命，还在美国导致2人遇难<ref name="TCR" />。小安的列斯群岛的农作物和牲畜遭受重大损失，加勒比多个国家和美国都有部分建筑物和基础设施受损<ref name="TCR" />。

=== 小安的列斯群岛 ===
丽丽以热带风暴强度吹袭小安的列斯群岛，当地风速大多低于飓风强度，但也有部分地点的阵风时速超过每小时119公里<ref name="TCR" />。上百毫米的降水引发多场致命的[[泥石流|泥石流]]<ref name="caribmud" />。部分建筑物质量不佳，许多民宅和商铺的屋顶被风刮落。该群岛蒙受的大部分经济损失都是香蕉作物受损。<ref name="relief1" />

[[圣卢西亚|圣卢西亚]]有至少75%的香蕉毁于一旦，数以百计的民宅被狂风破坏<ref name="caribmud" />。岛上供电、供水和电话几乎完全中断，公共服务系统受到重创<ref name="relief1" />。全岛共有4人丧生，损失总额估计为2000万美元（2002年美元）<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="relief1" />。

[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]有400余套民居受损，近50棵树被狂风刮倒。该国的香蕉作物也像圣卢西亚一样受到沉重打击，还有部分地区供电和电话服务中断，损失总额近20万美元（2002年美元）<ref name="relief1">{{Cite news | author = Caribbean Disaster Emergency Response Agency | title = Situation Reports:Caribbean:Tropical Storm Lili | publisher = Relief Web | year = 2002 | accessdate = 2016-04-06 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/cuba/tropical-storm-lili-situation-report-no-2 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306233148/http://reliefweb.int/report/cuba/tropical-storm-lili-situation-report-no-2 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-06 }}</ref><ref name="TCR" />。

[[格林纳达|格林纳达]]同样遭受中等程度破坏。1户民居的屋顶彻底被毁，另有14户受损。岛上中心医院的屋顶同样受损，另外还发生共计12次[[山崩|山体滑坡]]。<ref name="relief1" />岛上基础设施也受到轻度破坏，其中又以[[圣帕特里克区_(格林纳达)|圣帕特里克区]]灾情最重，共有3座桥梁受损或被毁，还有7根[[电线杆|电线杆]]倒塌，1条[[供水系统|主水管]]破裂。岛上供电一度全部中断，但南部地区由于电线杆的损伤程度较轻而得以迅速恢复。<ref name="relief1" />

与小安的列斯群岛的其它区域相比，圣文森特和格林纳丁斯群岛灾情严重。数以百计的民居和两所学校受损，罗斯霍尔警察局的屋顶也不翼而飞。<ref name="relief1" />不过，经济损失的大头仍然来自农业<ref name="relief1" />，全岛的损失总额约为4000万美元（2002年美元）<ref name="relief1" />。

=== 海地 ===
{{在海地产生降水最多的热带气旋|align=left}}
经过海地近海期间，热带风暴丽丽正在逐渐消散<ref name="TCR" />。气旋在该国产生瓢泼大雨，局部最高降雨量是在坎普佩兰（{{lang|en|Camp-Perrin}}）附近测得，超过410毫米<ref name="camp-perrin">{{Cite news | author = Organization for the Rehabilitation of the Environment | title = Hurricane Lili Was Accompanied by Torrential Rains As it Passed Over Haiti | publisher = Organization for the Rehabilitation of the Environment | year = 2002 | accessdate = 2016-04-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308200901/http://oreworld.org/flood/flood.htm | archivedate = 2016-03-08 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.oreworld.org/flood/flood.htm }}</ref>，导致河流泛滥，当地多幢建筑被淹，还有两人因降雨引发的泥石流丧生，另有两人在坎普佩兰周边地区发生的洪灾中溺毙<ref name="USAToday3">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | title = Lili killed 4 in Haiti; deaths unreported for a week | work = USA Today | accessdate = 2016-04-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150820063623/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/news/2002/2002-10-05-lili-haiti.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/news/2002/2002-10-05-lili-haiti.htm | date = 2002-10-05 | publisher = Gannett Co. Inc. | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-08-20 }}</ref>。洪灾还对庄稼和基础设施产生严重破坏，超过1700套民居受损，另有240套被毁。多条河流泛滥成灾，许多城镇和村庄被淹。<ref name="USAToday3" />

=== 牙买加 ===
热带风暴丽丽影响牙买加时正逐渐增强，岛上阵风时速超过110公里，降雨量超过610毫米，致使民房、庄稼和公共服务系统受到破坏<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="jamaicamon" />。

极端的降水导致该国大范围地区被淹，雪松谷是岛上测得降水最多的所在，达590毫米。严重的洪灾在岛上四处引发泥石流，夺走4条人命。作为该国主要出口作物之一，甘蔗也因洪灾受到毁灭性打击。<ref name="jamaicamon" />洪灾还对岛上大范围地区的基础设施构成破坏，所有的医院都因洪水受损，其中3所还因狂风出现结构性破坏<ref name="jamaica2">{{Cite news | author = Pan American Health Organization | title = Hurricane Lili in the Caribbean | publisher = World Health Organization | date = 2002-09-30 | accessdate = 2016-04-06 | archivedate = 2015-10-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151029095013/http://www1.paho.org/English/DD/PED/lili-hur.htm | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.paho.org/English/DD/PED/lili-hur.htm }}</ref>。另外，洪灾还导致厕所等污水源头污染供水水源，引起人们对灾后疾病爆发的忧虑<ref name="jamaica2" />。

=== 古巴 ===
10月1日，丽丽以二级飓风强度先后从青年岛和[[比那尔德里奥省|比那尔德里奥省]]登陆古巴。该国出现时速超过180公里的阵风，局部地区降雨量达150毫米，导致民居、商铺和农作物受损，另有1人遇难。<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="Cuba1">{{Cite news | author = International Federation of the Red Cross | title = Press Releases: Caribbean: Tropical Storm Isidore — September 2002, Cuban community left reeling by Isidore and Lili | publisher = Relief Web | year = 2002 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160406145455/http://reliefweb.int/report/cuba/cuban-community-left-reeling-isidore-and-lili | accessdate = 2016-04-06 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/cuba/cuban-community-left-reeling-isidore-and-lili | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-04-06 }}</ref>

古巴的建筑物及多种基础设施受到重大破坏，比那尔德里奥省和[[哈瓦那省|哈瓦那省]]灾情最为严重。共有4万8000户民宅受损，其中1万6000户失去屋顶。[[圣斯皮里图斯省|圣斯皮里图斯省]]的灾情相对较轻，只有945户民房受损，其中500户失去屋顶。包括[[关塔那摩省|关塔那摩省]]在内的几个古巴东部省份灾情与圣斯皮里图斯省类似。<ref name="Cuba2">{{Cite news | author = International Federation of the Red Cross | title = Situation Reports: Caribbean: Tropical Storm Isidore — September 2002, Caribbean: Hurricane Lili Information Bulletin No. 03/02 | publisher = Relief Web | year = 2002 | accessdate = 2016-04-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131109233641/http://reliefweb.int/report/cayman-islands/caribbean-hurricane-lili-information-bulletin-no-0302 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/cayman-islands/caribbean-hurricane-lili-information-bulletin-no-0302 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-11-09 }}</ref>古巴西部省份部分城镇的停电情况持续数周之久，停电又导致水泵无法工作，自来水因此中断，多个边远村庄只能人工送水<ref name="Cuba1" />。烟草和水稻作物受到灾难性破坏，但由于飓风伊西多尔在仅1周前来袭，因此人们难以确定到底这些损失中有多少是由丽丽造成<ref name="Cuba1" /><ref name="Cuba4">{{Cite news | author = Office of the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs | title = Caribbean — Tropical Storm Lili OCHA Situation Report No. 8 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131109105743/http://reliefweb.int/report/cuba/caribbean-tropical-storm-lili-ocha-situation-report-no-8 | publisher = Relief Web | year = 2002 | accessdate = 2016-04-06 | archivedate = 2013-11-09 | deadurl = no | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/cuba/caribbean-tropical-storm-lili-ocha-situation-report-no-8 }}</ref>。

=== 路易斯安那州 ===
[[File:Lili2002rainfilledwhite.gif|thumb]]
10月3日早上，丽丽以一级飓风强度从因特拉科斯特尔城附近登陆，并且还在逐渐减弱<ref name="TCR" />。当地阵风时速高达190公里，降雨量超过150毫米，还出现3.7米的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]，路易斯安那州一共遭受的经济损失超过7亿9000万美元（2002年美元）。共有23万7000人失去供电，近海多个石油平台被迫关闭1周之久。<ref name="Lili2" />农作物也受到重创，其中又以甘蔗灾情最重，损失总额有近1亿7500万美元（2002年美元）。由于气旋本身的规模较小，之前的警告又比较及时，该州没有人直接因风暴丧生。<ref name="Lili02">{{Cite news | author1 = Kent Kuyper | author2 = Marty Mayeaux | author3 = Montra Lockwood | author4 = Donovan Landreneau | author5 = Joe Rua | author6 = Lance Escude | author7 = Roger Erickson | title = Lili '02 | publisher = NWS WFO Lake Charles, Louisiana | date = 2002-10-18 | accessdate = 2002-12-26 | url = http://www.srh.noaa.gov/lch/tropical/lili/lili_rpt.htm | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20021226160502/http://www.srh.noaa.gov/lch/tropical/lili/lili_rpt.htm | archivedate = 2002-12-26 }}</ref>

气旋登陆的[[弗米利恩堂区_(路易斯安那州)|弗米利恩堂区]]受灾最为严重。时速超过190公里的阵风和高达3.7米的风暴潮共同影响，导致近4000户民居受到重创<ref name="Lili2" />。风暴潮在因特拉科斯特尔城引发的洪灾最为严重，单某直升机公司就有20幢建筑被毁。有1人在风暴过后死亡，另有20人因一氧化碳中毒入院治疗。<ref name="Lili2" />

[[File:Lili2002coastalflooding.jpg|thumb]]

[[阿卡迪亚堂区|阿卡迪亚堂区]]同样受到重创，除测得时速超过180公里的阵风外，该堂区还有5场[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]着陆<ref name="Lili2">{{Cite news | author = National Weather Service Forecast Office, Lake Charles, Louisiana | title = LILI | publisher = National Weather Service | year = 2002-10-16 | accessdate = 2003-04-17 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.srh.noaa.gov/lch/tropical/lili/lili_psh.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20030417141302/http://www.srh.noaa.gov/lch/tropical/lili/lili_psh.htm | archivedate = 2003-04-17 }}</ref>。数以千计的民居受损，其中超过2500套程度严重。堂区各地供电基本中断，另有2人受伤，还有1人在飓风过后丧生。堂区内的多所学校一共受到价值160万美元（2002年美元）的破坏<ref name="Lili2" />。

=== 密西西比州 ===
丽丽的外围[[雨带|雨带]]在密西西比州产生热带风暴强度大风和可观降水<ref name="LAlilisummary">{{Cite news | author = National Weather Service Forecast Office, New Orleans, Louisiana | title = Post Tropical Cyclone Report...Hurricane Lili | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | year = 2002 | accessdate = 2003-03-02 | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | url = http://www.srh.noaa.gov/data/NEW/PSH/newpshnew.1.txt | archivedate = 2003-03-02 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20030302233511/http://www.srh.noaa.gov/data/NEW/PSH/newpshnew.1.txt }}</ref>。[[帕斯卡古拉_(密西西比州)|帕斯卡古拉]]测得时速66公里的阵风，[[珀尔里弗县_(密西西比州)|珀尔里弗县]][[皮卡尤恩_(密西西比州)|皮卡尤恩]]的降雨量达到105毫米。州内还有多地停电，但程度较轻，绝大部分发生在南部地区。洪水一共对密西西比州的道路和建筑构成价值3000万美元（2002年美元）的破坏，该州没有人员因这场风暴遇难。<ref name="TCR" />

=== 美国其它地区 ===
飓风丽丽的残留还在继续产生暴雨，其中以[[阿肯色州|阿肯色州]]降雨量最高，达100毫米，风暴最终在该州同田纳西州边界附近逐渐消散，各地没有出现重大灾情。美国各州一共因飓风丽丽蒙受了8亿2000万美元损失。<ref name="TCR" />

== 善后 ==
[[File:Lili2002disasterdeclarationmap.jpg|thumb]]
风暴过去后，[[美国总统|美国总统]][[乔治·沃克·布什|乔治·沃克·布什]]宣布路易斯安那州为联邦灾区，以便该州获得联邦援助<ref name="disdeclaration">{{Cite news | author = Mike Brassfield | title = Hurricane Lili Runs Out of Steam | newspaper = St. Petersburg Times | date = 2002-10-04 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-04-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303171404/http://www.sptimes.com/2002/10/04/Worldandnation/Hurricane_Lili_runs_o.shtml | url = http://www.sptimes.com/2002/10/04/Worldandnation/Hurricane_Lili_runs_o.shtml }}</ref>。[[联邦紧急事务管理局|联邦紧急事务管理局]]在密西西比州和路易斯安那州共计设立3个网点，接收灾区民众的援助申请，到截止日期时一共收到15万3000份申请<ref name="153k">{{Cite news | author = Federal Emergency Management Agency | title = Louisiana Aid Deadline Looms, 153,000 Have Applied | publisher = Federal Emergency Management Agency | date = 2002-11-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120301211253/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=2751 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2012-03-01 | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=2751 | archivedate = 2012-03-01 }}</ref><ref name="fema35k">{{Cite news | author = The New Orleans Channel | title = Federal Emergency Management Agency Fans Out After Storms | publisher = WDSU | date = 2002-10-07 | accessdate = 2012-02-08 | archivedate = 2012-02-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120208042206/http://www.wdsu.com/news/1706286/detail.html | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.wdsu.com/news/1706286/detail.html }}</ref>。路易斯安那州最终一共获得3亿1100万美元援助金<ref name="311mil">{{Cite news | author = Federal Emergency Management Agency | title = Lili Recovery at More Than a Quarter Billion Dollars | publisher = Federal Emergency Management Agency | date = 2003-01-02 | accessdate = 2012-03-01 | archivedate = 2012-03-01 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120301211302/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=2762 | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=2762 }}</ref>。

来自8个州的上千名电力公司职工赶赴受灾最严重的地区协助恢复供电<ref name="power3">{{Cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120722040829/http://www.wtvy.com/home/headlines/110161.html | author = WTVY | title = Hurricane Lili Aid | publisher = WTVY | year = 2002 | accessdate = 2016-04-06 | archivedate = 2012-07-22 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wtvy.com/home/headlines/110161.html }}</ref><ref name="arkpower">{{Cite news | author = Melissa Simas | title = Utility Workers on Ready for Storm Damage | publisher = KAIT | year = 2002 | accessdate = 2016-04-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151228214634/http://www.kait8.com/Global/story.asp?S=959699&nav=0jshBbXu | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.kait8.com/Global/story.asp?S=959699&nav=0jshBbXu | archivedate = 2015-12-28 }}</ref>。有7个州向受灾的州赠送修枝剪，以便灾区尽快清除道路和输电线缆上的各种垃圾，加速救灾进程<ref name="cleco">{{Cite news | author = Cleco Corporation | title = Cleco Power | publisher = Cleco Corporation | year = 2002 | accessdate = 2016-04-06 | url = http://www.cmsgis.com/main/services/featuredclients.htm | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303172035/http://www.cmsgis.com/main/services/featuredclients.htm | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>。联邦紧急事务管理局向路易斯安那州的主要供电公司“{{lang|en|SLEMCO}}”提供860万美元赠款，用于补偿该州电网所受破坏的75%<ref name="power'sback">{{Cite news | author = [[联邦紧急事务管理局|Federal Emergency Management Agency]] | title = SWLA Electric Corp To Receive $8.6 million Federal Emergency Management Agency Public Assistance Grant | publisher = Federal Emergency Management Agency | year = 2002 | accessdate = 2012-03-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120301211310/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=2765 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=2765 | archivedate = 2012-03-01 }}</ref>。该公司一共花了4周时间才恢复所有用户的电力供应<ref name="powerbackon">{{Cite report | author = Storm Work | title = Helping Costumers and Communities | publisher = Storm Work | year = 2002}}</ref>。

飓风丽丽对路易斯安那州近海的湿地和屏障岛构成重大环境破坏。登陆点附近湿地中有大量鱼类死亡，附近的[[阿查法拉亚盆地|阿查法拉亚沼泽]]也有类似情况。登陆点以东多个屏障岛遭受的风暴潮最为猛烈，由此导致严重[[侵蚀作用|侵蚀]]。大量沙子在盐水湿地沉积，将植被掩埋。淡水湿地因大风和风暴潮受到严重破坏，有些更被彻底摧毁。严重的侵蚀导致墨西哥湾同陆地上的水体间形成新水道相连，由此又令陆地上的泻湖受到进一步侵蚀。<ref name="greennowbrown">{{Cite report | author = Gaye Farris | title = USGS scientists monitor coastal damage from Hurricane Lili | publisher = USGS | date = 2002-10-14 | accessdate = 2016-04-06 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304060008/http://www.eurekalert.org/pub_releases/2002-10/usgs-usm101102.php | url = http://www.eurekalert.org/pub_releases/2002-10/usgs-usm101102.php }}</ref>

=== 退役 ===
由于这场风暴在加勒比地区造成大量人员伤亡和重大财产损失，[[世界气象组织|世界气象组织]]于2003年春将其名称“丽丽”退役，今后永远都不会再在[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]命名时采用。用来取代的新名称是“劳拉”（{{lang|en|Laura}}），于[[2008年大西洋飓风季|2008年]]首度启用<ref name="wmo1">{{cite journal | author = [[世界气象组织|World Meteorological Organization]] | year = 2004 | title = Final Report of the 2003 Hurricane Season}}</ref>。此外，世界气象组织还曾考虑用“露西”（{{lang|en|Lucy}}）或“利西特”（{{lang|en|Lisette}}）来取代“丽丽”<ref name="wmo2">{{cite journal | author = World Meteorological Organization | year = 2004 | title = Replacement Names for 2003 Atlantic Hurricanes (Fabian, Isabel, and Juan) and 2002 Hurricane Lili}}</ref>。

